{"tid":2078733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔得啦。今日已經食到第五隻傻。","createTime":"2020-06-25T09:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:56:51.000Z","uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9823ff2f55b127d616c6bbc033f75dbdd10561","tid":2078733,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"唔知老母想點，話出面啲傻好平買三個送兩個<br />\n尋晚帶咗九隻傻返嚟<br />\n老竇食咗兩隻已經話唔得<br />\n阿妹從來都唔食傻<br />\n我而家已經食到第五隻傻，<br />\n我好辛苦，老母而家仲笑騎騎坐係張梳發到睇緊蘋果動睇得好開心<br />\n有冇人可以話俾我聽點樣食隻傻會好食啲？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0b01d3754b5851af2e8b1d1880edb388ba2d46","tid":2078733,"uid":345289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"放入氣炸鍋"},{"pid":"5bc99ef0d93a346087bb6e4080d0f7e5f1084d1a","tid":2078733,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0b01d3754b5851af2e8b1d1880edb388ba2d46","tid":2078733,"uid":345289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"放入氣炸鍋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3323d62638d1644cebe9057f5737036981dbaed","tid":2078733,"uid":330057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c0b01d3754b5851af2e8b1d1880edb388ba2d46","tid":2078733,"uid":345289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:23:46.000Z","msg":"放入氣炸鍋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T09:26:38.000Z","msg":"有冇啲可以依家即刻解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75408d8abb489301937b2829df3484fe464c7db0","tid":2078733,"uid":345289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3323d62638d1644cebe9